  "subject": "WIP - Add DNS Designate to OOM",
  "commit_message": "WIP - Add DNS Designate to OOM\n\nInstead of having the underlyaing infrastructure providing\nDNS Designate, which is not always easy to have, due to the\nfact is really new. This patch provide support to deploy\na small OpenStack with only Keystone and Designate, along\nwith all micro-service required to make this work.\n\nChange-Id: Id9a5161fa04b35e80e784811352ea67139050961\nIssue-ID: OOM-588\nSigned-off-by: Alexis de Talhouët <adetalhouet89@gmail.com>\nSigned-off-by: Jerome Doucerain <jerome.dourcerain@bell.ca>\n",
